    "c"
  ],
  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Dividing both sides of <math><mi>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi></math> by <em>m</em> yields <math><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>F</mi><mi>m</mi></mfrac></math>.</p><p>Choices A, B, and D are incorrect.</p>",
